1. DEVICE FLASHING RISK WARNING (设备刷机风险警告)

   This software is designed for flashing Qualcomm devices in EDL mode.
   Flashing devices carries inherent risks including but not limited to:
   
   本软件用于在 EDL 模式下刷写高通设备。刷写设备存在固有风险，包括但不限于：

   - Permanent device damage ("bricking") / 永久性设备损坏（"变砖"）
   - Loss of data / 数据丢失
   - Voiding device warranty / 使设备保修失效
   - Security vulnerabilities / 安全漏洞

   THE USER ASSUMES ALL RISKS ASSOCIATED WITH USING THIS SOFTWARE.
   用户承担使用本软件的所有风险。

2. DISCLAIMER OF WARRANTY (免责声明)

   THE SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED "AS IS", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND.
   本软件按"原样"提供，不提供任何保证。

